data.description: !!WAY BELOW APPRAISED VALUE!! Entertaining All Offers! Appraisal available with accepted offer. Come get your piece of the mountains in this spacious but cozy Cabin that over looks Mt. LaConte! This cabin is 10 minutes from Dollywood and 20 minutes from Gatlinburg The bottom floor has a Bedroom and Bathroom along with the Kitchen and breakfast nook that's attached to the living room. The second level has a Bedroom and 1/2 bath that has provisions to be completed into a full bath. the loft overlooks the living area and the uncovered portion of the deck. The back porch features a wet bar and covered patio while the rest of the wrap around deck brings in your unobstructed views of and complete privacy. Schedule your showing today and see what this cabin has to offer. Cabin needs some minor repairs, HOA information can be found at shieldsmtnpoa.org. all of the documents are on file there. Call me or ask your agent to fill you in.
